{
  "stem": "20616.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After school I worked at a dry cleaners delivering clothes, picking up clothes, delivering.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before school, I delivered newspapers and during vacation or on weekends very often, I shined shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in Washington Heights, it wasn't such an affluent area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not too many people could afford to have their shoes shined, so I had to travel quite a bit with a chair and a box to an area and usually settled on midtown Manhattan, which was slightly more affluent.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It only cost a nickel to go to-- by subway to go there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But by the same token, a shoeshine only was a nickel on weekdays.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On weekends, it was a dime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were times when I didn't have any customers and I didn't have a nickel to go back with the subway so I had to go from 86th Street to 153rd Street carrying a chair and my shoeshine box and walking home without having done anything.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And once I remember my mother visited me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a terribly hot day and I was sitting on the sunny side of the street where the sun hit the-- she said, why don't you go over to the shady area and sit there and wait for customers?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody has their shoes shined on that area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's not a busy area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she went into a store, she bought me a Coke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she spent-- I chided her, you spent a nickel on a Coke for me and I didn't have a single customer yet today.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't even have the car fare-- made the car fare to go home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You should have saved that nickel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So everything-- every nickel counted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When we bought-- hm?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I need you to stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We're at the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
